Event:     E_MOVE_INV

Called:    Whenever a containers (even rooms) inventory is changing, a 
           move_inv event is called.

Usage:     Add an event (see add_event), create an event handling function, 
           that will be called if the event occurs:
	   void function(object o, object from, object to) { ... }

Arguments: object o    - the object that _has_been_ moved
           object from - the former environment
           object to   - the new environment
